data.description: This stunning split-level home boasts three bedrooms, two full baths, and an inviting open-concept living area. The dedicated downstairs features a spacious family room, complemented by a two-car garage. With approximately 2000 sq. ft. of finished living space, the residence offers a perfect blend of comfort and style. Enjoy the outdoors on the expansive deck, and for pet lovers, the fenced backyard with a convenient gate adds an extra touch of charm. Wonderful country living within Westwood Schools.  Counter tops will be replaced prior to close.  They have been ordered and a swatch is available during showings.
